		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Lightning</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Lighting" title="Lighting">Lighting</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">"Lightening" redirects here. For the cosmetic lightening of skin, see <a href="/wiki/Skin_lightening" title="Skin lightening" class="mw-redirect">Skin lightening</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Lightning_(disambiguation)" title="Lightning (disambiguation)">Lightning (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
