<p><a name="Historical_scientific_research" id="Historical_scientific_research"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lightning&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Historical scientific research">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Historical scientific research</span></h2>
